      <title>Manjaro翻墙</title>
      <link href="/config/b3b81b15.html"/>
      <url>/config/b3b81b15.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- build time:Wed May 15 2019 11:26:14 GMT+0800 (China Standard Time) --><h1 id="Manjaro翻墙"><a href="#Manjaro翻墙" class="headerlink" title="Manjaro翻墙"></a>Manjaro翻墙</h1><h2 id="1-普通加密方式"><a href="#1-普通加密方式" class="headerlink" title="1.普通加密方式"></a>1.普通加密方式</h2><ol><li><p>安装ss-qt5</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S shadowsocks-qt5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>配置ss-qt5</p></li></ol><h2 id="2-使用chacha20-ietf-poly1305加密shadowsocks"><a href="#2-使用chacha20-ietf-poly1305加密shadowsocks" class="headerlink" title="2.使用chacha20-ietf-poly1305加密shadowsocks"></a>2.使用chacha20-ietf-poly1305加密shadowsocks</h2><ol><li><p>安装shadowsocks-libev</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S shadowsocks-libev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>配置</p><p>修改后为如下配置：注意后面的”fast_open”: true</p><p>要加入</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;server&quot;:&quot;server_ip_address&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;server_port&quot;:8368,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;local_port&quot;:1080,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;password&quot;:&quot;linuxssh.com&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;timeout&quot;:60,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;method&quot;:&quot;chacha20-ietf-poly1305&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;fast_open&quot;: true</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="3-让终端走代理"><a href="#3-让终端走代理" class="headerlink" title="3.让终端走代理"></a>3.让终端走代理</h2><ol><li><p>安装polipo</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S polipo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>配置polipo</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo vim /etc/polipo/config.simple</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将socksParentProxy，socksProxyType，proxyAddress的#号去掉。</p><p><img src="data:image/png;base64," data-original="b3b81b15/Screenshot_20181212_021635.png" alt="Screenshot_20181212_021635"></p></li><li><p>启动polipo服务</p><p>zsh：sudo systemctl start polipo.service</p><p>bash：sudo systemctl start polipo</p></li><li><p>查看状态</p><p>bash：sudo systemctl status polipo</p><p>zsh：sudo systemctl status polipo.service</p></li><li><p>设置终端代理变量</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">export http_proxy="localhost:8123"</span><br><span class="line">export https_proxy="localhost:8123"</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>设置git代理</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global http_porxy 'localhost:8123'</span><br><span class="line">git config --global https_porxy 'localhost:8123'</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><!-- rebuild by neat -->]]></content>
      
      
